prodNameC: “儀器實驗室”寶石比米爾3000專用卡匣(血液氣體/血容比)
ingredientsDesc:
The internal waste bag, which collects used blood and solutions throughout cartridge life, keeps biohazard to a minimum.
The cartridge contains solutions with the following approximate concentrations:
Reference Solution A 	pH 6.9 organic buffer; pCO2 = 65 mmHg,
pO2 = 0 mmHg, Na+ = 155 mmol/L
K+ = 2 mmol/L, Ca++ = 0.2 mmol/L,
surfactant and inert preservative
Reference Solution B	pH 7.40 organic buffer; pCO2 = 35
mmHg, pO2 = 190 mmHg, Na+ = 135mmol/L, 
K+ = 6 mmol/L, Ca++ = 2.0mmol/L, 
surfactant and inert preservative buffer
Reference Solution C	For low level oxygen calibration, conditioning the glucose and lactate sensors, and cleaning the sensor chamber; contains aqueous solution of Na+ and K+ salts, surfactant and inert preservative, organic buffer, and pCO2
Reference Solution D	KNO3 = 1000 mM/L, AgNO3= 1 mM/L, and surfactant
applicantAddr: 臺北市內湖區堤頂大道2段501號4樓
efficacy: 本拋棄式卡匣為寶石比米爾3000系統(GEM Premier 3000 System)之主要配件、提供作為快速全血檢驗分析之用，可提供有關血液氣體、血容比等測量及計算參數。
